{"tid":2118303,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"2020/2021 polyu Physiotherapy 物理治療集中討論區","createTime":"2020-07-21T11:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T00:08:47.000Z","uid":248054,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0dedb230351208f66f9c55d93d9ca8ba3c93c61f","tid":2118303,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"hello 大家好 又到放榜時刻<br />\n<br />\nQ：今年收幾多人？<br />\nA：150人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：Admission score 係幾多？<br />\nA：自2017開始計Best 6，今年繼續收best 6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2016 Average Best 5 29.9<br />\n2017 Average Best 6 34.5<br />\n2018 Average Best 6 34.5<br />\n2019 Average Best 6 34.4<br />\n<br />\n有關於 Admission Score 嘅官方資料都可以喺下面呢個網搵到：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/jupas/programme-requirements\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww51.polyu.edu.hk%2Feprospectus%2Fug%2Fjupas%2Fprogramme-requirements&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=8585fbe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www51.polyu.edu.hk/eprospectus/ug/jupas/programme-requirements</a><br />\n<br />\n2016-2018 Admission Figure<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.polyu.edu.hk/asadm/jupas/admission_figures.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwixpun5xJXjAhWS7WEKHd0qC38QFjAAegQIBhAC&amp;usg=AOvVaw2OCM5wkDxrrJQLZN7Q67h7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2Fasadm%2Fjupas%2Fadmission_figures.pdf%26ved%3D2ahUKEwixpun5xJXjAhWS7WEKHd0qC38QFjAAegQIBhAC%26usg%3DAOvVaw2OCM5wkDxrrJQLZN7Q67h7&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23RjxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=e89ed6cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.polyu.edu.hk/asadm/jupas/admission_figures.pdf&amp;ved=2ahUKEwixpun5xJXjAhWS7WEKHd0qC38QFjAAegQIBhAC&amp;usg=AOvVaw2OCM5wkDxrrJQLZN7Q67h7</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：計分有冇weighting呀？<br />\nA：參照返上年嘅內部計分標準，其實冇一個官方既資料，所以下面呢個只係估算，可能同真實既有些少出入，今年未必完全跟足曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中 Eng Phy Bio &times; 10<br />\nMath L.S. &times; 7<br />\nOthers &times; 5<br />\n<br />\nQ：無讀 Phy Bio 入唔入到？<br />\nA：絕對可以！只要乘完個 weighting 夠就得。PT有唔少朋友仔都冇讀Phy/Bio，Year 1 Sem 1嗰陣會同其他醫療科嘅同學一齊讀返啲基礎Bio野，比心機就好容易pick up 到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：Interview 重唔重要？<br />\nA：Interview主要係用黎揀啱啱好夠分入嘅人，所以對啲分去到average嘅人就唔太大影響，而如果個分太高或者太低都唔會安排interview，但記得有嘅話就一定要去啊，如果唔係就入唔到架啦。Interview 平常心面對就得，多數圍繞行內或者業來面對緊嘅問題，或者一啲關於醫療體制嘅嘢， 想知多啲歡迎喺下面再問。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：物理治療同職業治療有咩分別？<br />\nA：物理治療同職業治療同屬康復治療科學，但用黎治療患者嘅方法就大有不同。物理治療係用除咗藥之外嘅方法，好似超聲波、電、冷熱、水力、手法治療、針灸，改善病人嘅活動能力，亦都負責預防病人嘅活動能力出問題。最主要針對病人身體機能方面，嘗試令到病人嘅身體機能回復正常水平。<br />\n<br />\n職業治療就針對病人嘅生活能力，包括工作，自理，娛樂嘅能力，透過唔同嘅活動以及為病人度身訂做設計用具 ，令病人重拾或者保持佢嘅 functioning，可以好好咁做番佢哋本身嘅『職業』，同時提高佢哋嘅生活質素，以及令佢哋可以有尊嚴咁生活(留意職業治療對職業嘅定義係所有對病人有意義而有目的性嘅行動，所以職業治療並唔係醫職業病！！)。<br />\n<br />\n舉個簡單嘅例子：我作為一個平常人，咁我嘅職業就要食飯，但有一日我撞車整到右手，令我右手唔可以攞起匙羹食飯，PT就可以幫我回復翻手部活動能力，令我隻手可以揸翻起隻匙羹，喺隻手可以完全揸返匙羹之前，OT就會就我受傷嘅程度 ，透過設計一啲特殊嘅餐具，又或者係訓練，幫助我喺復原嘅過程當中自己食得番飯。<br />\n<br />\n總括嚟講，物理治療師多數 focus 喺 physical level ，工作比較專一；職業治療師同時 focus physical cognitive mental level。"},{"pid":"52b0b14408aeec2144f47d06093fb29ba013eed9","tid":2118303,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n今晚一齊打721國際戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1982796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1982796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e586a9441a2181bf6e792a6ae64e451d5a55f707","tid":2118303,"uid":251531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"想問34645677 <br />\nElective : Phy Chem Econ M2 入唔入到🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"348f